    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lankan Transport Board employees sacked in Yali",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan Transport Board's Jaffna road workers went on strike on Sunday 24th.",
        "Last Friday around 9 pm, both the driver and the guard of the 57-route ECO bus from Jaffna to Colombo were attacked by the Kalkamuwa Road ECO road workers in Thaladagama area.",
        "They strongly condemned the attack and demanded that appropriate action be taken against the employees who carried out the attack."
      ],
